{
  "id": "5b573a24fd8eb10014678ceb",
  "title": "近い目標と遠い目標の解像度の違い",
  "created": 1532443177,
  "updated": 1532499331,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5b573a24fd8eb10014678ceb",
      "text": "近い目標と遠い目標の解像度の違い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443177,
      "updated": 1532443202
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573a43aff09e0000258944",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/b8bc47c198e5bba3aac4e1b8bd8f221a]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443204,
      "updated": 1532443204
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573a42aff09e0000258942",
      "text": " 遠い目標ほど範囲が広い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443203,
      "updated": 1532443288
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573a95aff09e0000258945",
      "text": " 台風の進路予想図の[たとえ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443286,
      "updated": 1532443343
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573b46aff09e000025894a",
      "text": "  わかりやすく円で書いてるけど、ある時点での状況はこの図だと時間軸に直交する線分になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443462,
      "updated": 1532443540
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573ad4aff09e0000258947",
      "text": " 遠い未来の予想になるほど、不確実要素が増えていくから",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443348,
      "updated": 1532443375
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573b9aaff09e000025894c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443546,
      "updated": 1532443546
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573b9aaff09e000025894b",
      "text": " 遠い未来を近い未来と同じ解像度で予測しようとすると、より高い正確さが求められる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443546,
      "updated": 1532443743
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573c44aff09e000025894d",
      "text": "  それが可能だったらそもそも近未来の予測ももっと正確にできる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443717,
      "updated": 1532443749
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573c65aff09e000025894e",
      "text": "  アキレスと亀",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443750,
      "updated": 1532443753
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573c72aff09e000025894f",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/ca831c5a3b95a0f40a0d4fc4cb443b57]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443763,
      "updated": 1532443765
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573c97aff09e0000258953",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443799,
      "updated": 1532443799
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573c93aff09e0000258951",
      "text": " 遠くなればなるほど、予期しない障害物が現れる可能性が高まる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443796,
      "updated": 1532477314
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573cbfaff09e0000258954",
      "text": " 無理に詳細な目標を定めても、予期しない障害物に出会って方針転換が必要になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443839,
      "updated": 1532477315
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573ce0aff09e0000258955",
      "text": "  方針転換は悪ではないのでどんどんやればいい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443872,
      "updated": 1532477325
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573d1daff09e0000258957",
      "text": "   が、予定していたプランが潰れることに対して人間は割と心の痛みを感じるものである",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443934,
      "updated": 1532477327
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573d0baff09e0000258956",
      "text": "   なので、そもそもそんなに詳細に決めないほうがいい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443916,
      "updated": 1532477338
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57bf9aaff09e0000b6a352",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532477339,
      "updated": 1532477339
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57bf9aaff09e0000b6a351",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532477339,
      "updated": 1532477339
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573c74aff09e0000258950",
      "text": " 近い未来を遠い未来と同じ解像度で予測すると、大雑把すぎる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443765,
      "updated": 1532477464
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57c017aff09e0000b6a353",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/856c9963d718252787727a74a6e2c438]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532477464,
      "updated": 1532477465
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57c019aff09e0000b6a354",
      "text": "  なのでもっと詳細にせよというフィードバックを受けることがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532477465,
      "updated": 1532477502
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57c03faff09e0000b6a356",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532477503,
      "updated": 1532477503
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57c03faff09e0000b6a355",
      "text": "結果として、もっと詳細にせよ、と、詳細にするな、の[両方向のフィードバック]が発生する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532477503,
      "updated": 1532477682
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57c0daaff09e0000b6a357",
      "text": " #中庸 の図と同じ構図",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532477659,
      "updated": 1532499331
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573b23aff09e0000258949",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/24800a7b4632dcfb1e93678750342097]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443428,
      "updated": 1532477693
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57c0fcaff09e0000b6a358",
      "text": " 相反する指示を受けているように感じて混乱する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532477693,
      "updated": 1532477735
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57c160aff09e0000b6a359",
      "text": " もしくは詳細すぎる遠い未来の目標に対して「もっと曖昧にせよ」という指示ではなく「本当にそうなるのか？」というフィードバックがされる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532477793,
      "updated": 1532479276
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57c54caff09e0000b6a35a",
      "text": "  この時、ほんとうにそうなることを示そうとして根拠となる情報を集めて詳細化しようとする本末転倒なことが起きる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532478796,
      "updated": 1532479347
    },
    {
      "id": "5b57c774aff09e0000b6a35b",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532479348,
      "updated": 1532479348
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573b23aff09e0000258948",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443428,
      "updated": 1532443482
    },
    {
      "id": "5b573a43aff09e0000258943",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1532443204,
      "updated": 1532443204
    }
  ]
}